<plot>Developer J. Bricket Armstrong is out to buy up all the land in Hondo Valley. but rancher "Pop" Robinson won't sell his because of a promise he made his son, killed in WWII, and he also is housing a stranded band of show-business troupers. But, foreclosure is on the horizon, but the troupers put on a Big Show, and rodeo-performer Jack Norman kicks in his winnings from the Smoky River Rodeo to save the old Homestead.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?502784</url></doc>
